						               													<description>Risky Business is a quiz game with a healthy dose of bluffing. The goal is to correctly answer as many questions as possible. However it is also necessary to stake your answer at the right time.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;The game is played in rounds of five questions. All players bet money in each round. The player that can give the most correct answers and at the same time dares to stake it all the way will win the pot. The players are only aware of how many questions they have answered correctly themselves which means bluffing is a critical part of the game. Players can also use action chits to gain advantages over their opponents which lends the game an extra level of strategy.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;In spite of the game's English title it is only available in Swedish.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;The game was nominated to &amp;Aring;rets spel 2009 (Game of the year 2009 in Sweden).&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
